<div><strong><font size="2" face="Arial"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Position: <font color="#000000"><span style="color: black">Business Intelligence Analyst</span></font></span></font><font color="#000000"><span style="color: black">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></font></strong></div>
<div><strong><font size="2" face="Arial"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Location: <font color="#000000"><span style="color: black">Columbus</span></font><font color="#000000"><span style="color: black">, OH</span></font></span></font></strong></div>
<div><strong><font size="2" face="Arial"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Duration: 5+ Months</span></font></strong></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong>Interview Process: Phone, then In-Person Required</strong></font></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></div>
<div><strong><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Arial">Requirements:&nbsp;</span></font></strong></div>
<ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience in data warehousing and business intelligence </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">High proficiency in understanding relational and dimensional data models </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Proficiency in SQL including the use of SQL editors, stored procedures, database triggers and optimizing SQL statements </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience with Oracle 9i or higher </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Broad understanding of reporting technologies, including reporting suite management, report visualization, design and development, dashboard visualization , design and development, and analytical modeling, design and development </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience in tuning/caching reports, and service configuration </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Minimum two years knowledge of and experience with Business Objects toolsets, including Universe Designer, Web Intelligence, Crystal Reports, and Crystal Xcelsius, as a designer, developer, and administrator </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience with Business Objects Enterprise XI R3 </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Strong strategic skills, the ability to lead in the adoption of reporting, dashboard, and analytics technologies and toolsets, standards and best practices </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Proven tactical skills, the ability to move tactical decisions towards strategic initiatives </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Demonstrated ability to work both independently and within a team </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Ability to collaborate effectively with a broad base of business and technology associates </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Ability to work effectively with a broad range of internal and external customers </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Ability to handle difficult situations; work as a team to resolve issues and to help &ldquo;firefight&rdquo; during crisis situations </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Willingness and ability to mentor and train NetJets team member to assume Reporting Lead position when ready </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Excellent written and oral communication skills </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Excellent organizational and time management skills </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Demonstrated ability to handle multiple assignments simultaneously </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Demonstrated ability with Microsoft desktop tools, including Word, Visio, Excel, Access, PowerPoint, Project, and Outlook</span></font></li>
</ul>
<div><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></div>
<div><strong><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Arial">Desired Skills:</span></font></strong></div>
<ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Excellent knowledge and considerable development experience with one or more of the following:</span></font></li>
</ul>
<div style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.25in"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Arial">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hyperion Brio </span></font></div>
<div style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.25in"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Arial">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SQR</span></font></div>
<ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience in large-scale data warehouse deployment </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience in metadata management and Business Objects Data Integrator toolset </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience in creating and maintaining portlets </span></font></li>
    <li style="color: black"><font size="2" color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Experience in user experience design and/or designing web sites</span></font></li>
</ul>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Thanks</span></font></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></div>
<div><font size="2" face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial">Best Regards</span></font></div>
